videos.headline: Rosier takes it to the house for early Miami TD
videos.description: Miami QB Malik Rosier goes practically untouched five yards into the end zone to open up scoring.

videos.headline: Rosier throws a dime for another Miami TD
videos.description: Malik Rosier throws a perfect 38-yard pass to WR Jeff Thomas, putting Miami up 14-0.

videos.headline: Rosier runs for the 2-yard Miami TD
videos.description: Malik Rosier keeps the ball himself to increase the Miami lead.

videos.headline: Toledo gets on the board with a 7-yard strike
videos.description: Toledo's Mitchell Guadagni throws a strike to Diontae Johnson, narrowing Toledo's deficit to 21-7.

videos.headline: Toledo cuts the deficit with rushing TD
videos.description: Toledo running back Art Thompkins hustles into the end zone for a 5-yard Toledo touchdown.

videos.headline: Dallas rushes for another Miami TD
videos.description: Miami running back DeeJay Dallas picks up the pace as he runs for a 19-yard Miami touchdown.

videos.headline: Toledo's Johnson scores 2nd TD of game
videos.description: Toledo's Diontae Johnson goes untouched for a 40-yard touchdown, shortening Toledo's deficit to 28-21.

videos.headline: Rosier throws a 5-yard lob for a Miami TD
videos.description: Malik Rosier throws a perfect lob pass to WR Lawrence Cager for another Hurricane touchdown.
